your time does this take?

00:28:42.090 --> 00:28:44.100
BRIAN ROBERTSON: Yeah,
10 different circles

00:28:44.100 --> 00:28:44.950
would be a lot.

00:28:44.950 --> 00:28:46.680
Most people,
practically speaking,

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:48.800
in companies running
with Holocracy,

00:28:48.800 --> 00:28:52.070
you might have people in two
or three circles-- maybe four

00:28:52.070 --> 00:28:52.600
or five.

00:28:52.600 --> 00:28:54.480
But more than
that's really rare.

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:57.990
It means they're invited to
