00:29:12.580 --> 00:29:14.560
when you show up with
attention and you

00:29:14.560 --> 00:29:16.790
take the time to go to a
meeting and you address it,

00:29:16.790 --> 00:29:18.590
what you're doing is
changing the structure

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:20.760
so that tension
