00:40:23.980 --> 00:40:24.940
strategic thinking.

00:40:24.940 --> 00:40:28.510
And if so, what sorts of
circles-- what roles would

00:40:28.510 --> 00:40:31.784
you have to achieve that goal.

00:40:31.784 --> 00:40:33.700
BRIAN ROBERTSON: Yeah,
definitely, absolutely.

00:40:33.700 --> 00:40:35.074
So, again, it's tension driven.

00:40:35.074 --> 00:40:36.490
So if somebody has
a attention of,

00:40:36.490 --> 00:40:39.160
man, I think we need to be
looking at longer term, bigger

00:40:39.160 --> 00:40:40.650
picture, strategic stuff.

00:40:40.650 --> 00:40:41.190
Great!

00:40:41.190 --> 00:40:42.220
Process that tension.

00:40:42.220 --> 00:40:43.780
Maybe we need to create a role.

00:40:43.780 --> 00:40:46.180
We have roles like a
